title: Trump CIA nominee wanted to withdraw over interrogation role
text:
Trump CIA nominee wanted to withdraw over interrogation role 3:48am IST - 01:36
President Donald Trump's nominee to lead the CIA, Gina Haspel, sought to withdraw over concerns about her role in the agency's interrogation program. Tamara Lindstrom reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
